<div class="receipts">
	<div class="receipts__container container">
		<div class="receipts__title">
			<h2>Новые поступления</h2>
			<div class="receipts__title-buttons">
				<button class="receipts__title-button_left g-title-button">{% include "assets/svg/arrowleft.svg" %}</button>
				<button class="receipts__title-button_right g-title-button">{% include "assets/svg/arrowright.svg" %}</button>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="receipts__corusel">
			<div class="receipts__corusel-book">
				<div class="receipts__book-img">
					<img src="img/1.png" alt="">
					<span>Бестселлер</span>
					<span>1+1=3</span>
				</div>
				<div class="receipts__book-genre g-book-genre">
					<span>Корпоративное право</span>
				</div>
				<div class="receipts__book-description g-book-description">
					<span>Инвестирование: способы, риски, субъекты : монография</span>
				</div>
					<div class="receipts__book-author g-book-author"><span>Майфат А.В.</span></div>
				<div class="receipts__book-price g-book-price">4 450 ₽ </div>
				<div class="receipts__book-button g-book-button">
					<button>
						{% include "assets/svg/bagorange.svg" %}
						<span>В корзину</span>
					</button>
					<button>
						{% include "assets/svg/mark.svg" %}
					</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>